    <item>
      <title>卡尔西（Kalshi）的顶级律师退出成为SEC的Doge团队的领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/kalshi-s-top-lawyer-quits-to-become-leader-of-doge-team-at-sec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，衍生品交易所Kalshi Inc.的前首席监管官Eliezer Mishory正在领导美国证券交易委员会的总督团队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/kalshi-s-top-lawyer-quits-to-become-leader-of-doge-team-at-sec</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 15:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯说，即使英国确保了我们的交易，特朗普的关税也会伤害英国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/rachel-reeves-says-donald-trump-s-tariffs-will-hurt-uk-even-if-us-deal-secured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政总理雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的总理说，即使部长们成功地确保对英国商品的豁免，英国也将受到美国关税的全球影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/rachel-reeves-says-donald-trump-s-tariffs-will-hurt-uk-even-if-us-deal-secured</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 15:15:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗重申与我们进行间接核谈判意愿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/iran-reiterates-willingness-for-indirect-nuclear-talks-with-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外交大臣重申了与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对该国核计划的政府进行间接谈判的意愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/iran-reiterates-willingness-for-indirect-nuclear-talks-with-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 15:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促访问南非商业领袖平衡贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-urges-visiting-south-africa-business-leaders-to-balance-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据来自非洲大陆最大的经济体的商业和劳工领袖说，南非和美国之间的破碎关系取决于平衡的贸易，他们与华盛顿的美国政客会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-urges-visiting-south-africa-business-leaders-to-balance-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 14:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员被民主党强迫参加贸易战争投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/perilous-vote-looms-for-gop-senators-as-trump-launches-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党参议员将很快被迫做他们避免的事情：在贸易战总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）煽动贸易战争上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/perilous-vote-looms-for-gop-senators-as-trump-launches-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 14:56:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟眼睛紧急计划将经济免受特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/eu-plans-emergency-measures-to-shield-economy-from-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，欧盟正在准备一套潜在的紧急措施，以支持其部分经济的部分，这些措施可能会受到美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的全面关税的最大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/eu-plans-emergency-measures-to-shield-economy-from-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 14:38:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院在很大程度上支持Biden-er-fda在调味vap上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/supreme-court-largely-backs-biden-era-fda-on-flavored-vapes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院在很大程度上支持食品和药物管理局在拒绝出售风味蒸发产品的申请方面，支持该机构在乔·拜登（Joe Biden）担任总统期间对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）采取这种方法的不确定性的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/supreme-court-largely-backs-biden-era-fda-on-flavored-vapes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 14:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市市长亚当斯的腐败案被法官永久驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/adams-judge-permanently-dismisses-criminal-case-against-mayor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官驳回了针对埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）的腐败指控，使案件永久性结局，并结束了一系列非凡的事件，这些事件播下了司法部内的不和谐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/adams-judge-permanently-dismisses-criminal-case-against-mayor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 13:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>McMorrow进入密歇根州参议院比赛，目标工人阶级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/mcmorrow-enters-michigan-senate-race-targets-working-class-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根州参议员马洛里·麦克莫罗（Mallory McMorrow）在2022年受到了激烈的讲话的关注，他宣布她将竞选由退休民主党加里·彼得斯（Gary Peters）撤离的美国参议院席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/mcmorrow-enters-michigan-senate-race-targets-working-class-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
